Class Exam

java.lang.Object
com.panotify.model.Exam
public class Exam extends Object
Represents an exam in the PaNotify system. An exam contains questions, is associated with a course, and has properties such as deadline, duration, and total score.
Version:
1.0
Author:
PaNotify Team
